BLACKJACK LAYOUT

1. Find and learn to use the card library
  A. Learn to deal cards
  B. Learn how to use value
  C.
2. Create the ability to deal cards randomly to player and dealer.
  A. Every player gets two 
  B.Every Dealer gets 2 one face up.
  C.
3. Take the input of the card value and compare it to the dealers.
  A. Is value > 21 = bust
  B.if d_value < p_value = win
  C.
4.Create the Buttons 
  A. Create a hit button
  B. Create a Stand Button
  C. Create a Doublle Button
5. Create the Ability to Wager
  A. Player Starts with 2000
  B. Player can waiger as much as they wish within those boundaries
  C. Make a goal of 25,000
  
  
